# Security patterns to block in pre-commit
# Scans for common secret/PII leaks before code is committed

# === API Keys & Tokens ===
ghp_[a-zA-Z0-9]{36}
sk-proj-[a-zA-Z0-9-]{20,}
sk-ant-[a-zA-Z0-9-]{20,}
AKIA[0-9A-Z]{16}
xoxb-[0-9A-Za-z-]{20,}

# === Hardcoded paths (platform-specific) ===
C:\\Users\\[a-zA-Z]+\\\.openclaw\\secrets
C:/Users/[a-zA-Z]+/\.openclaw/secrets
/home/[a-zA-Z]+/\.openclaw/secrets

# === Private keys & credentials ===
PRIVATE KEY
wallet\.key
\.pem
password\s*=\s*['\"][^'\"]+['\"]
